<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>عَطاء بن يزِيد<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">أَرْبَعَة:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١ -<span class="c5"> عَن أبي سعيد:</span> إِذا سَمِعْتُمْ الْمُؤَذّن.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٢ -<span class="c5"> وَعَن عبيد الله بن عدي:</span> يَسْتَأْذِنهُ فِي قتل رجل من الْمُنَافِقين.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٣ -<span class="c5"> وَعَن أبي أَيُّوب:</span> لَا يحل لمُسلم أَن يهجر.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٤ -<span class="c5"> وَعَن أبي سعيد:</span> من يتصبر يصبره الله.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>سَالم بن عبد الله<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">ثَمَانِيَة:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>